Class CORBAConnection

java.lang.Object

org.eclipse.persistence.sessions.remote.corba.sun.CORBAConnection
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class CORBAConnection extends RemoteConnection
This class exists on on the client side which talks to remote session controller through RMI connection.
